frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts a giant burger being constructed by miniature workers. The towering burger, complete with multiple layers of patties, cheese, and bacon, is being assembled with the aid of a crane and blowtorches. The setting resembles a construction site, complete with tools and a conveyor belt of lettuce.
frames.description: The scene is set in a playful, imaginative construction site where miniature workers are assembling a gigantic burger. The workers use construction equipment like cranes and blowtorches to build the burger, creating a humorous juxtaposition between food and construction.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts a giant burger being assembled by miniature construction workers. The towering burger, complete with multiple layers of bacon and cheese, is being lifted by a crane, while workers use blowtorches to melt the cheese. The setting is a playful blend of a construction site and a kitchen.
frames.description: The image portrays a creative fusion of culinary and construction themes, where a massive burger is being built like a skyscraper. Miniature workers are actively engaged in assembling the burger, using tools and machinery typically found on a construction site.
